                    comment = "Some code extracted from rollapply in the zoo package"))
Description: Lazy and tidy resampling methods using quosures to delay computation 
  of samples until they are needed. The implemented methods include 
  bootstrap (simple, weighted, Bayesian), and cross-validation (leave-one-out,
  leave-p-out, k-fold).
